==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea bream
<hw>Sea" bream`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
several species of sparoid fishes, especially the common European
species (<spn>Pagellus centrodontus</spn>), the Spanish (<spn>Pagellus
Oweni</spn>), and the black sea bream (<spn>Cantharus lineatus</spn>);
-- called also <altname>old wife</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea brief</ent>⟦br⟧
